Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說血腥約翰左肩膀有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我的籌碼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再檢查是否有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-周四晚上八點見面  -好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要你的幫助  -沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就會認為你是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和簡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再懷疑我是血腥約翰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后絕對不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的確定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -此案結束的時候我要在場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您這句話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高興不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰  有個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三個點  就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻動手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始脫吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他們倆那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們別動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墻邊站著  快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫消防部門和急救人員過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴他們這里有多人傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒線拉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把你的手電筒給我  我進去  -給你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員  我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -發生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里剛剛發生了爆炸  急救人員已經在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會救治你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不許動  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手舉起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就開槍了  快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  我不明白你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明顯搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯往哪邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  我們必須得找到史密斯  他是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找人幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能聽到我講話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生說簡的情況穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒受什么重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是醒不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現場發現了三個人的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化驗確認是布萊特·斯特爾斯  雷·哈弗內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和托馬斯·麥卡利斯特的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為核攻擊都干不掉布萊特·斯特爾斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸體都被燒焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鑒證科還是提取出了DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸官那邊將結果與醫療記錄進行比對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已確認三位死者正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特爾斯  哈弗內和麥卡利斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那史密斯呢  有人看到他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒  瑞斯比和范佩爾正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道在這兒能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  不過我確實得喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能幫我去買一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上要開始聯合追捕史密斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你該趕快去抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想待在這里  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是...  -周和其他組員應付得來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要拒絕執行我的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在這里陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我聽清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令你現在馬上離開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶領你的組員一起去抓捕史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  簡  那個呼叫按鈕在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫護士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在認為  是血腥約翰帶去的炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要殺死簡和其他嫌犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但怎么布下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是血腥約翰隨身偷偷帶進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪現場小組從墻上發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸彈外殼的碎片  碎片非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說明火藥密度高  威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定不是自制的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  我猜是軍用級別的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就說明我們能夠追蹤到來源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是最有可能的來源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查查看最近他們中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誰曾報告丟失過炸藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有線索了嗎  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本在史密斯逃走前曾擊中過他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是帶著槍傷在四處逃竄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫院看到槍傷必須向警方報備
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他不能去看急診
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  他需要一個不會聲張的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯一直在薩克拉門托工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了一下全市他負責過的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所在的緝毒小組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年在薩克拉門托市南部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕過阿列克·拉夫羅夫醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個非法開具奧施康定[強力止痛藥]處方的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}Dr. Feelgood指的是常給病人開出興奮劑等安慰性藥方的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后呢  -案子審判不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證物丟失  拉夫羅夫被無罪釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以史密斯很清楚在哪能找到一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會報警的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我們馬上去查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家里發生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昏迷多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他肩膀上的紋身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只他有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麥卡利斯特身上也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經死了  斯特爾斯和哈弗內也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-還有伯特侖  -伯特侖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也有那個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才還在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才就站在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他  他還一直想讓我離開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的衣服呢  -別著急  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事  我們沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡  簡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全州境內發出里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蓋爾·伯特侖的通緝令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  就是伯特侖局長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近時務必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們持有武器  十分危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們其中一個就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}伊凡·拉夫羅夫醫生診所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}今日停業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請趕快離開  女士  警察辦案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子彈還在你體內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話了  趕緊取出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定不吃點止疼藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃  我要保持警覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就隨你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他快喊破喉嚨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會成為麻煩的  你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛從加調局得到消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有幾個探員正要來這里找史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我們該怎么辦  -趕緊了事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你進去搞定他  加調局的人來了我拖住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從后面把他帶出去  在那干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他逼我這么做的  我是無辜的  -閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一走我就會報警的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不想惹麻煩  -閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是組織的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎  你為什么不給我們打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來真怪  因為我不相信你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要信任你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來幫你的  你能走路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得給他縫好  不然會失血的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是科德羅警探  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比探員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是薩城警局的  負責柯克蘭槍擊案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是格蕾斯·范佩爾探員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎么來薩城南部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們跟一條線索過來抓里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是  血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來我們快你們一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人已經進去抓他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我們看住后面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用  我們能搞定  -你確定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我們不是加調局的  但是我們也是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在醫生辦公室外面  史密斯好像在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有警察在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  你仔細聽清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要相信任何一名執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不能相信  明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去后面四周看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車就在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近有個安全屋  干凈衣服  一名醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出城的路線也準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也對某個人說過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎  后來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朝他后背開了六槍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你沒事吧  -沒事  你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯趁亂逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個警探也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  他們想殺史密斯和我們  這是為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -看看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -讓他看看左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓瑞斯比把他襯衣脫了看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本想讓你看他的左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  他肩上有那個紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒  這是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把他帶回局里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓任何人接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到襲擊你們的警察身份了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我們抓到的那個  保羅·魏海根警官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當警察六年  模范警察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受過幾次表彰  沒紀律問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那另一個  科德羅警探呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打電話問了他隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說他一小時前請了病假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒查到伯特侖的行蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就著重調查我們抓到的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許簡會弄清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人派你殺里德·史密斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什么要殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那紋身是怎么回事  有什么意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不善言辭  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禍從口出嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壞消息是  你的表情控制得不夠好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們要玩個你演我猜的小游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴你些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用表情告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是對是錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷過東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背著女友偷腥過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打過她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡施暴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從沒打過女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一個由警察和其他政府官員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組成的秘密組織成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為維護那個組織的利益犯過罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員也是組織成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織派你去那個診所殺他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局局長蓋爾·伯特侖也是組織成員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等級太低了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探員是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肩上的紋身是組織成員的標志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有個暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們成員間用來識別身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我腦子里滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個腐敗警察的秘密組織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死之前對我說了"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄希望于你也是成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果他也有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸報告里應該有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信什么報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要親眼看到才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓周去檢查尸體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很有可能帕特里奇已經下葬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓周帶上鏟子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的人在找史密斯  伯特侖在外逃中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底誰是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伯特侖還是史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看著他們的眼睛才能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驗尸官兩天前把尸體送過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謀殺案被害人是吧  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜就是  所以才會一直留著他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你今天來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就什么都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷特·帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫把手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒之前都會給他們穿上好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周發了張照片過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這說明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯處理好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們差點就在診所那里解決他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局的人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可真會跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這兒等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  托馬斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您很久沒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯現在可能在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試著追蹤他手機上全球定位信號
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經關閉好幾個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他這樣的腐敗聯調局警察一定會有一次性手機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夫羅夫醫生說他還沒縫合史密斯的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在還帶著槍傷四處走動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不管他在哪兒  情況一定不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終一定會被人發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但是發現他的警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了  我們誰都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾探員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會殺了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第十八大道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在市中心  給周打電話  他應該在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我們這就來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯聯系加調局了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用了組織給他的一次性手機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們監聽了那部手機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加調局的人去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行  他在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離這兒不遠的小巷子里  我們運氣很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他認識你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識  在診所那兒他沒看見我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你現在就是加調局探員了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起去嗎  說不定挺好玩兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去了  我還有別的事要處理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-到時再碰頭吧  -行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次別失手了  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  長官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探員
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在嗎  范佩爾探員派我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧斯卡·科德羅探員  加調局的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來接你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保證我安全
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天吶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.18,0:24:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到車尾去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會真以為你能逃脫得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂事的  幫個忙  自己爬后備箱里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再讓我歇會兒  行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后備箱里去歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.54,0:24:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別逼我動手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.47,0:25:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上車
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個條件  我要求完全豁免權
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你們放過我  否則我一個字都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.23,0:25:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.81,0:25:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.28,0:25:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過但愿你能在你的朋友追上你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出這棟大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你坦白我們所要的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保證把你安排在遠離加州的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.57,0:25:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保證你安全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前  我傷了背
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了幫我表兄搬張該死的沙發
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.02,0:25:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生給我開了點兒止痛片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.61,0:26:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.29,0:26:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上癮了  自己都沒覺察到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.31,0:26:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.88,0:26:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.00,0:26:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在卡森泉把一個小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼到了一條巷子里  然后我的癮上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.13,0:26:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全意識不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為有人跟蹤我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.70,0:26:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開槍打死了一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她十二歲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.16,0:26:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當地警察采了我的血樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.73,0:26:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們有目擊證人  我當時死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后來了個警探
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.61,0:26:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他找到我說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.57,0:26:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可以把這事擺平
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.10,0:26:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后真的擺平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血樣  目擊證人  都擺平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們擺平那事兒以后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.56,0:26:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局還給我頒發了一枚獎章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他們"到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.76,0:26:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們自稱為"布萊克組織"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎  燃燒著煌煌的火光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}此處摘自郭沫若譯本
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來自布萊克的詩作
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.12,0:27:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概某人很喜歡他的作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.25,0:27:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織里還有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.17,0:27:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一個有秘密需要掩蓋的執法人員
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如你的毒癮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你有麻煩了  向他們求助
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.19,0:27:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當他們讓你做點什么  你就得照做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.83,0:27:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.53,0:27:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組織有頭目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我所接觸的小團體
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.43,0:27:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我猜測
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.58,0:27:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個組織至少有數百人  甚至上千人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就沒人發覺這一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.25,0:27:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮑勃·柯克蘭知道這事  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.58,0:27:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快直接招了吧  說出來給你自己一個解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.08,0:28:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.71,0:28:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.92,0:28:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.79,0:28:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.10,0:28:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是布萊克組織的成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.49,0:28:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.73,0:28:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰有一個追隨者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.17,0:28:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗貝卡·安德森
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前殺了幾個你們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  山姆·博斯科和他的小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他們
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.49,0:28:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人曾要我搞到聯調局證件
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.98,0:28:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便他們能進入加調局
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.62,0:28:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰或者他的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.73,0:28:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潛入加調局  對麗貝卡下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.48,0:28:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然為他們提供了幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.17,0:28:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在幫助一個連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:29:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰讓你搞那些證件的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  我只是接到一通電話
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.18,0:29:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是組織的運作方式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.16,0:29:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永遠不知道上線是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.45,0:29:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.53,0:29:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們能保證我的安全 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.30,0:29:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要看情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.25,0:29:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你殺害了我的妻子和女兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有殺你的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我母親的名義起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他承認了謀殺罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.94,0:29:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥約翰絕不會這么容易崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.46,0:29:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是做戲也不會如此
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.47,0:29:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果史密斯不是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.93,0:29:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味著我們還得繼續追查
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.46,0:29:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.28,0:29:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是布倫達·夏垂克的繼任者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.60,0:29:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公共關系部嗎  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝大家能在臨時通知后趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.84,0:29:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是加調局顧問派翠克·簡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.50,0:29:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他將就血腥約翰一案的進展
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進行通報
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.63,0:30:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱作血腥約翰的連環殺手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.47,0:30:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺害了我的妻子和女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后  我們一直在全力追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們很高興地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.33,0:30:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終于確認了他的身份與面目
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.70,0:30:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,執法部門負責人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.02,0:30:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋爾·伯特侖局長  就是血腥約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他持有武器  極度危險
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.56,0:30:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人發現他的行蹤  切勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.79,0:30:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即致電加利福尼亞州調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.48,0:30:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請輪流提問
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉請回避  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.14,0:31:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們能談談這事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.35,0:31:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關于伯特侖是血腥約翰的事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.58,0:31:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果讓簡找到他  簡會殺了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就沒問題嗎  把頂頭上司殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.78,0:31:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我無所謂  -我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.35,0:31:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.81,0:31:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我們保持步調統一
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.08,0:31:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是覺得有點詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.95,0:31:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖吸煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.69,0:31:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.25,0:31:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候人們會收到打火機作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.60,0:31:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.83,0:31:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個閃存盤
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.72,0:31:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.57,0:31:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}納帕谷  七仙女酒廠
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.08,0:31:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盤里只有一個文件
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:31:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有密碼保護
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.98,0:32:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得硬破解
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒極了  我一直想用用我的新FPGA
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[FPGA: 現場可編程邏輯門排列]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.75,0:32:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.84,0:32:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  還是別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.03,0:32:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}加州調查局  內部數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.33,0:32:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}加州調查局  內部數據庫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.10,0:32:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[亂碼]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來像個清單
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是名單  你能破譯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.01,0:32:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.43,0:32:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但破解謎題是簡的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.66,0:32:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到時候發給他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來一杯這個  這種威士忌口感很純
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.57,0:32:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了很多泥煤烘烤麥芽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.98,0:32:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯  能加點冰塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.74,0:32:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你確定嗎  這可是上好的蘇格蘭威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我確定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙跟你有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}連環殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.51,0:33:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.89,0:33:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在去酒吧的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.19,0:33:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速巡警封鎖了高速公路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.89,0:33:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一跑我們就能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.28,0:33:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他要是躲起來怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.50,0:33:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖在柑橘高地殺了個酒保
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在那邊的姨媽有間房子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.21,0:33:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得他在那里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:33:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她六個月之前搬到養老院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.81,0:34:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她家現在空著
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.33,0:34:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來是個不錯的藏身之處  地址在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.50,0:34:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露絲瑪麗街1408號
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.44,0:34:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就到  讓周和快速反應小組過去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.30,0:34:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在這嗎  -在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓卡爾和幾個人去后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.42,0:34:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他無處可逃  -我們能信他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.95,0:34:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了他們的肩膀  沒有紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.42,0:34:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你來這里干什么  我沒叫薩城警局派特警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.25,0:34:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要我們來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.57,0:34:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那邊建一個指揮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.74,0:34:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著  各位  這里由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.38,0:34:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是從北區來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.65,0:34:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跨了整個城了  到底是什么情況
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.54,0:34:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他干的  他把他們叫來的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.71,0:34:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特侖把特警叫到自己這來干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.53,0:34:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不止召來了一個特警組
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.15,0:34:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把整個特警隊都召來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:34:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋后有整整一隊別的警察在準備
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無法控制局面了  頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.88,0:35:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在他們之中  伯特侖混在他們之中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.90,0:35:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要逃跑  我們得停止行動
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.22,0:35:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰都不許走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.17,0:35:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人都不許走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.83,0:35:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.82,0:36:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得吃點東西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.45,0:36:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃中餐么  我知道有一家很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.64,0:36:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  聽起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.47,0:36:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們在屋里發現了伯特侖的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.15,0:36:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是有人在他去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.92,0:36:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在房子里放好了特警服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.06,0:36:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把城里所有的特警和
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.55,0:36:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速反應小組叫了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.90,0:36:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是誰打的電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.79,0:36:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是個能在暗中一呼百應的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.65,0:36:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布萊克組織
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.52,0:36:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.78,0:36:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.16,0:36:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下電話  離開你們的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.87,0:36:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.67,0:36:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這里特別探員主管特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.72,0:36:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.22,0:36:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局監管部門探員  丹尼斯·阿爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.85,0:36:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說一遍  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.32,0:36:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.13,0:36:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名極其危險的逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.18,0:36:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你們想協助
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.95,0:36:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這個所謂的執法部門的長官
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.27,0:36:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.88,0:37:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是重大犯罪組織的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.69,0:37:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個組織里也有聯調局探員
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.03,0:37:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對  所以局里把我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.75,0:37:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從德州奧斯汀調過來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.84,0:37:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾你們這個爛攤子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.02,0:37:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯邦法官簽署的令狀
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聯調局將立即關停你們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.63,0:37:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.54,0:37:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除任職
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即生效
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.23,0:37:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能這么做
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來收集證據的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.62,0:37:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.72,0:37:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.42,0:38:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.63,0:38:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是聯調局的丹尼斯·阿爾伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.07,0:38:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是派翠克·簡了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們關停了我們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.66,0:38:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到時候會找你問話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過可以緩一緩  我們會在這兒待一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.57,0:38:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別出城
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.77,0:38:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有個兇手要抓
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.20,0:38:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這案子現在歸我們管了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.95,0:38:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有過機會  但是搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.99,0:38:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你當時是真想抓他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.76,0:38:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我最喜歡的杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.87,0:38:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  幸會  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.61,0:38:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在怎么辦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.74,0:38:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.85,0:38:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩爾在伯特侖的閃存里找到了一些加密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要不要從那開始查
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.71,0:38:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  浪費時間而已  結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.58,0:38:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這里沒我們的事兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.40,0:39:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧  休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.86,0:39:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會放棄  我不信你會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.80,0:39:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我不是放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.04,0:39:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是放手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.69,0:39:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前的情況我們已經無法掌控了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.78,0:39:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持聯絡  好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.93,0:39:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切  我很抱歉
